      <div class="rc"><span class="rc-icon">&#128293;</span><div class="rc-title">Smoke backing into the room when you light the fire</div><div class="rc-desc">The most common sign of a blocked or sooted flue. A professional clean restores draw immediately.</div></div>
      <div class="rc"><span class="rc-icon">&#9888;&#65039;</span><div class="rc-title">More than 12 months since the last professional clean</div><div class="rc-desc">Annual cleaning is the correct standard for any fireplace or heater in regular seasonal use. Book before you need the fire running nightly.</div></div>
